      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "To investigate whether the MB-PLS derived correlation clusters are structurally related, we used retention time (RT) matching and mass-to-charge ratio (m/z) differences to find possible isotopologues and adducts both within and across the assays. We call these structurally linked features structural groups.",
