      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/10_1371_journal_pcbi_1011814__task_002/010",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Finally, the structural groups were compared to the correlation clusters and visualized using network plots.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms network plot visualizations and silhouette score usage ('selected the optimal number of clusters by the highest mean silhouette score'), but does not explicitly mention dendrograms, heatmaps, or silhouette plots as outputs. Network plots are the primary visualization mentioned.",
