      "asbval:note": "Paper describes a 'structural search tool' that performs adduct/isotopologue matching and clustering, but does not name it 'MamsiStructSearch'. The tool is part of the MAMSI workflow but the specific name 'MamsiStructSearch' is not confirmed in the passages. The GitHub repo reference (kopeckylukas/py-mamsi) suggests this may be the correct tool name, but it is not explicitly stated in the paper text.",
