      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "This experiment shows that the MAMSI workflow enabled the discovery of cross-assay structural relationships that would not be possible to detect using univariate methods. Furthermore, many of those cross-assay groups match biological signatures reported in the literature.",
      "asbval:note": "The paper demonstrates that network-based visualization of structural relationships aids in understanding multi-assay coherence and compound structure.",
