    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/hierarchical-clustering-dendrogram-interpretation/000",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "We then applied agglomerative hierarchical clustering using the farthest point (complete) linkage and selected the optimal number of clusters by the highest mean silhouette score.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper uses silhouette-score optimization for dendrogram flattening, but does NOT compare this to constant-threshold methods. The paper applies only one flattening strategy (silhouette optimization), not a comparison of alternative strategies. The research question claims a comparative evaluation that is not present in the paper.",
