      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Here, we propose the MAMSI (Multi-Assay Mass Spectrometry Integration) workflow that utilizes an MB-PLS model for integrating multiple metabolomic LC-MS assays.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms MAMSI exists and is a Python framework for LC-MS metabolomics integration. However, passages do not mention or describe a 'MamsiStructSearch.get_correlation_clusters()' method or a 'flat_method='silhouette'' parameter. The paper describes silhouette-based cluster selection but does not document the specific API or method signature claimed in the card.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1021-acs-analchem-5c01327",
